# Components List – Landmine Detection Robot

## Core Controller

* ESP32 DevKit (WROOM/WROVER)
* ESP32 CAM

## Sensors

* Ultrasonic Sensors (x4) – Obstacle detection
* Metal Detector Module – Detect buried metallic objects
* IR Sensors – Short-range obstacle detection
* IMU Sensor – Orientation and motion tracking
* Temperature Sensor (TEP20N) – Environmental monitoring

## Actuators

* DC Motors (x2 or x4 depending on design)
* BTS7960 Motor Driver – High current motor control

## Power System

* 3S3P Li-ion Battery Pack
* 3S BMS (20A)
* Boost Converter Module
* LM2596 Voltage Regulator

## Output/Alert System

* Buzzer
* LED Indicators

## Additional Modules

* ESP32-CAM (for ML-based detection - planned)
* SD Card Module – Data logging

---

## Notes

* System designed for multi-sensor fusion
* ML model integration planned using Edge Impulse
* Optimized for low power consumption and real-time response
